    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? This car has been such a joy to own and is still in really solid shape! It runs like a dream and has been super well-cared for over the years. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for its next adventure. Perfect for your daily commute or fun weekend getaways! Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
